    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-08-04</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-09-10T18:38:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Prosecutorial Tools Improvement Act of 2007 - Amends the Controlled Substances Act to impose enhanced criminal penalties for serious violent felonies committed during and in relation to any drug trafficking crime.</p><p>Amends the federal criminal code to: (1) impose additional restrictions on the release of persons charged with certain firearms offenses; and (2) establish limitation periods for prosecuting certain noncapital crimes of violence and terrorism.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
